title: BRIEF-Arcus Biosciences Files For IPO Of Up To $100 Million
text:
Feb 16 (Reuters) - Arcus Biosciences Inc :
* ARCUS BIOSCIENCES INC FILES FOR IPO OF UP TO $100 MILLION – SEC FILING
* ARCUS BIOSCIENCES INC SAYS IT INTENDS TO APPLY TO HAVE ITS COMMON STOCK LISTED ON NEW YORK STOCK EXCHANGE UNDER THE SYMBOL “RCUS”
* ARCUS BIOSCIENCES INC SAYS CITIGROUP, GOLDMAN SACHS & CO. LLC, LEERINK PARTNERS ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO
* ARCUS BIOSCIENCES INC SAYS PROPOSED IPO PRICE IS AN ESTIMATE SOLELY FOR CALCULATING SEC REGISTRATION FEE Source text : ( bit.ly/2EzAQFO )
